# MMS Demo Application

**Metro Fleet Mileage Management System** - Win-the-bid demonstration application.

## Overview

This is a demonstration application for Metro fleet preventive maintenance (PM) management. It showcases CSV-based PM projection over a 10-year horizon with an infinite canvas interface using semantic zoom levels (strategic έΗΤ tactical έΗΤ operational views).

**Key Features:**
- Drag-and-drop PM rescheduling with constraint validation
- "Bow-wave" risk visualization (fleet maintenance clustering)
- WebGL-powered infinite canvas rendering with deck.gl
- State management with @belt/tools

## Getting Started

```bash
# Install dependencies
bun install

# Start development server
bun dev

# Build for production
bun run build

# Lint code
bun run lint

# Format code
bun run format
```

## Project Structure

```
src/
