έΦεέΦΑέΦΑ App.tsx               # Root component
έΦεέΦΑέΦΑ store/                # @belt/tools state machines
έΦεέΦΑέΦΑ engine/               # PM projection algorithm (CRITICAL)
έΦεέΦΑέΦΑ import/               # CSV parsing and validation
έΦεέΦΑέΦΑ canvas/               # deck.gl infinite canvas
έΦεέΦΑέΦΑ components/           # React UI components
